      "span_text": "The performance of the Schedule-based Optimized Node Recharging Model (SONRM) with the incorporation of Recharge Scheduling Algorithm (RSA) has been evaluated and the obtained results are compared with the two existing approaches, Enabling Temporal and Distantial Priority (TADP) and Hybrid Clustering Charging Algorithm (HCCA)"
